<HEADLINE>
<P>
HEALTH CARE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Conrad's cartoon "The Bob and Elizabeth (Dole) Show" (March 29) is another 
great example of Conrad's liberal speak.According to Conrad, the Clintons want 
to give everyone free health insurance.  
</P>
<P>
 The Clintons are not going to give us anything unless they plan to pay for it 
out of Whitewater and pork-belly profits. As for it being free . . . what a 
joke. President Clinton wants employers to pay 80% of the cost, which in turn 
they will pass on to the consumer. Translated, you and me baby! Gee thanks, 
Bill. 
</P>
<P>
 HERB COOK 
</P>
<P>
 Balboa 
</P>
</TEXT>
