<TEXT>
<P>
 Arkansas becomes the 30th school to win the NCAA men's basketball title. 
</P>
<P>
 In the 56-year history of the championship, there have been 19 one-time 
champions and 11 multiple champions, including Duke. 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 Color analysis: Every school to win the NCAA title since 1980 has featured 
either red or blue as a school color. Michigan State (1979) wore green. MIKE 
DOWNEY 
