shortly after their escape. They denied having attacked the man, authorities 
said. 
</P>
<P>
 The youths were held briefly at the East Los Angeles sheriff's station but 
were moved to Los Padrinos Juvenile Hall, where they are being held on 
suspicion of attempted murder, authorities said. 
