</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Fortune Petroleum Corp., an Agoura Hills energy concern, reported larger net 
losses in its fourth quarter and year that ended Dec. 31, which it said was 
primarily due to onetime, non-cash charges in the fourth quarter triggered 
mainly by low oil prices. 
</P>
<P>
