year-earlier loss of $288,000. Its quarterly revenue rose 54%, to $892,000 from 
$578,000. 
</P>
<P>
 For all of 1993, the company lost $3.65 million, while its revenue rose 31% to 
$2.83 million. In 1992, it lost $198,000 on $2.16 million in revenue. 
