 Revenue for 1993 doubled to $11.3 million, from $5.53 million for 1992. 
Incomnet said it expects revenue to grow to about $30 million this year, 
boosted by its telephone subsidiary, NTC, in which Incomnet has invested about 
$5 million during the last two years to prepare. 
