<BYLINE>
<P>
By Jack Searles 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Nancy Mayerson, former public relations director of the Murphy Organization, 
an Oxnard advertising and public relations firm, has launched her own agency in 
Westlake Village. 
</P>
<P>
 Clients of the new company, Mayerson Marketing & Public Relations, include 
