<TEXT>
<P>
 La Mirada 19, Crespi 2 -- La Mirada scored 12 unearned runs in the first 
inning of the St. Paul tournament game. Crespi (8-4-1) committed five errors. 
</P>
<P>
 Alemany 11, St. John Bosco 6 -- Indian Gus Lira had two hits and two runs 
batted in for Alemany (9-3) in a St. Paul tournament game at Cal State Los 
Angeles. 
</P>
