 Camarillo 1-5, Huntington Beach 0-3 -- The Scorpions (10-2) swept a nonleague 
doubleheader. Jefflyn Spahr scored the only run of the first game on Tiffany 
Joynt's two-out single. Melanie Richardson (9-1) pitched a one-hitter. In the 
second game, Jessica Ziese hit a bases-loaded triple. 
